Here is a complete, interactive, single-file HTML presentation for PBuddy.

It features a deep navy blue and electric cyan design, smooth animations, keyboard navigation (left/right arrows), a progress bar, and a built-in "Speaker Notes" toggle so you can practice your pitch.

You can save this code as an .html file (e.g., pbuddy-pitch.html) and double-click it to open it directly in your web browser (Chrome, Safari, Edge, etc.).

